# Quantum Auth Framework - Implementation Walkthrough

## Summary

Successfully implemented a **Quantum-Seeded Dynamic QWT (Quantum Web Token) Framework** - a production-ready authentication system bridging IBM Quantum computing with Java Spring Boot enterprise security.

---

## Architecture Implemented

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    IBM[☢️ IBM Quantum] --> Miner[🐍 Python Miner]
    Miner -->|RPUSH| Redis[(⚡ Redis)]
    Redis -->|LPOP| API[☕ Spring Boot]
    API --> Dashboard[⚛️ React]
```

